      / ---------------------------crousel--------------------------------
    #home-v1-header-carousel.carousel.slide[data-ride="carousel" data-interval="2000"]
      .carousel-inner
        .carousel-item.active
          figure
            = image_tag "header-slider/home-v2/header-slide.jpg", class: "d-block w-100", alt: "Library Management System"
          .container
            .carousel-caption
              h3 Welcome to the Library Management System!
              h2 Streamline Your Library Operations
              p Manage your library’s inventory, patrons, and transactions with ease. Our system offers a comprehensive solution for efficient library management, ensuring that every book and user is accounted for.
        .carousel-item
          figure
            = image_tag "header-slider/home-v2/header-slide.jpg", class: "d-block w-100", alt: "Efficient Management"
          .container
            .carousel-caption
              h3 Effortless Book Management
              h2 Keep Track of Your Collection
              p From cataloging new arrivals to tracking book loans and returns, our system simplifies every aspect of book management, helping you keep your library organized and accessible.
              .slide-buttons.hidden-sm.hidden-xs
                a.btn.btn-primary[href="#"] Learn More
                a.btn.btn-default[href="#"] Get Started
        .carousel-item
          figure
            = image_tag "header-slider/home-v2/header-slide.jpg", class: "d-block w-100", alt: "User-Friendly Interface"
          .container
            .carousel-caption
              h3 User-Friendly Interface
              h2 Intuitive and Accessible
              p Designed with ease of use in mind, our system offers an intuitive interface for both staff and patrons. Enjoy a seamless experience as you navigate through your library’s features and functionalities.
              .slide-buttons.hidden-sm.hidden-xs
                a.btn.btn-primary[href="#"] Explore Features
                a.btn.btn-default[href="#"] Contact Us
      ol.carousel-indicators
        li.active[data-target="#home-v1-header-carousel" data-slide-to="0"]
        li[data-target="#home-v1-header-carousel" data-slide-to="1"]
        li[data-target="#home-v1-header-carousel" data-slide-to="2"]

