  section.welcome-section
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-6
          .welcome-wrap
            .welcome-text
              h2.section-title
                | Welcome to the LBMS
              span.underline.left
              p
                | Welcome to the Library Book Management System (LBMS), where we offer an extensive collection of books and resources for every reader. Our platform allows you to explore a wide range of genres and categories, ensuring that you'll find something that piques your interest. Whether you're a student, researcher, or casual reader, LBMS is designed to make your library experience seamless and enjoyable.
                | 
                | From classic literature to modern bestsellers, our system is built to provide easy access to all your favorite reads. With advanced search features and personalized recommendations, finding your next book is just a click away. Join us as we revolutionize the way you interact with your library resources.
              a.btn.btn-primary[href="#"]
                | Learn More
        .col-md-6
          .welcome-image
            = image_tag "wellcome-image.jpg", class: "align-right", alt: "Library Welcome Image"
  
